# Cross-origin API. In-app browsers (KakaoTalk 등) block this cross-origin call, so
# Android KakaoTalk auto-redirects to Chrome (main.jsx) and iOS shows a banner asking
# the user to open Safari — in a real browser the cross-origin call works.
#
# ▶ When the Cloudflare same-origin proxy (Worker or Origin Rule for
#   momentum.geol2.com/api/*) is live, switch this to an empty value so calls go to the
#   same origin — then in-app browsers work too and the auto-redirect can be removed.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.geol2.com
